  {
    "id": "TANX",
    "name": "坦克斯",
    "type": "Ancient",
    "act": "Act 3 - Glory",
    "description": "收下我的力量，去吧，杀戮！",
    "preconditions": null,
    "options": null,
    "pages": null,
    "epithet": "嵌合兽之王",
    "dialogue": {
      "Returning": [
        {
          "order": "0-0r",
          "speaker": "ancient",
          "text": "收下我的力量，去吧，杀戮！"
        },
        {
          "order": "1-0r",
          "speaker": "ancient",
          "text": "今天，必有浴血之战！"
        }
      ],
      "Ironclad": [
        {
          "order": "0-0",
          "speaker": "ancient",
          "text": "多么残暴的怒火！是施行暴力的时间了！"
        },
        {
          "order": "1-0r",
          "speaker": "ancient",
          "text": "收下我的力量！！摧毁你的敌人吧！"
        }
      ],
      "Necrobinder": [
        {
          "order": "0-0",
          "speaker": "ancient",
          "text": "一堆骨头？？那你显然需要我的力量！"
        },
        {
          "order": "1-0r",
          "speaker": "ancient",
          "text": "没有肌腱，没有肉，没有蛋白质！你靠什么战斗？？"
        }
      ],
      "Regent": [
        {
          "order": "0-0",
          "speaker": "ancient",
          "text": "你和伟大的坦克斯一样，也是橙色！？？"
        },
        {
          "order": "0-1",
          "speaker": "character",
          "text": "众所周知，橙色是最符合帝王的颜色！"
        },
        {
          "order": "0-2",
          "speaker": "ancient",
          "text": "橙色了不起！威风凛凛！！"
        }
      ],
      "Silent": [
        {
          "order": "0-0",
          "speaker": "ancient",
          "text": "是猎手！我会把你细小的利爪磨得更利！！"
        },
        {
          "order": "1-0r",
          "speaker": "ancient",
          "text": "弱小的绿色人类啊！成为站在巅峰的掠食者吧！"
        }
      ],
      "First Visit": [
        {
          "order": "0-0",
          "speaker": "ancient",
          "text": "收下我的力量，去吧，杀戮！"
        }
      ]
    },
